    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Windows having primary divisions into three parts, usually reserved for windows divided vertically. Group of three small windows next to each other, separated from one another by small columns or posts. Also 'triplet windows'.</Note_Text>
